summary: The Menendez brothers, Lyle and Erik, convicted of murdering their parents in 1989, are in the spotlight once again as their case undergoes reevaluation. Lil Durk is not the only suspect in the case, as five other alleged members of his entourage have also been charged in connection with the shooting. The arrests come as part of a broader investigation into gang violence in Chicago, which has seen a rise in shootings and homicides in recent years.
